VINTAGE STUFF 💨🔥🇨🇺
In love with elegant & sophisticated Diplomáticos No. 1 made in 2001
It’s amazing feeling to hold this discontinued cigar! 
I just hope that trend of long & slender cigars will be back 🙏🏻
Life is Beautiful 👍🏻
